      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un juhsu Biḣiaṡchana un neem/no Lohpem/nn no wiſſeem\nBeedinaschana tai irr pahr wiſſeem Semmes Swehreent ar jums:\nfeem Semmes Swehreem / nn no wiſſeem / kas no Schkirsta irr\npahr wiſſeem Putneem appakſch isgahjuſcht/ihs wiſſeem Semmes\nDebbes/nn wiſſu/ kas kust wirs Swehreem.\nSemmes/ nn pahr wiſſahm Si-\nvim Juhrâ/ tee irr juhsäs Roh-\nâs dohti."
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiſſ kas kust nn dsihwos\nr/ laid irr jums par Barribu/\nt ka saltu Sahli eſinu es jums\niſſu nodewis."
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tomehe to Meeſti ſawa Aſ-\nn/ eeſſch ka winna Dsihwiba\njums ne buhs ehſt."
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo patcefi es praſſischu juh-\nAffini / (to Affini) juhsäs\nſihwibas / no wiſſeem Sweh-\nm griibu es to praſſibt / ir no\nweetu Rohkahm/ nn no iſkatra\nohkas/ kas winna Brahtis irr/\nwiſſchu es ta Zilweka Dsih-\nbu."
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kas Zilweka Affini iṣgahſch/\nAffinin buhs zaar Zilwekeem\nahſtahm tapt / jo wiſſch irr\nZilweku pehz Deewa Gihmi\nrijis."
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet juhs anglojeetees / nn\nrojeetees / nn rohdajtees pa\nlkeem wirs Semmes/ nn war-\netees wirs tahs."
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Deews runnaja us Noii/\ns winna Dehleem ar winnu/\nidams:\nBet redſi/ es eezeltu ſawu\nribu ar jums / nn ar juhsu\nmmimu pehz jums."
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ar wiſſu dsihwu Dwa-\nkas ar jums irr / no Put-"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un es uzeltu ſawu Der-\nribu ar jums : Un wiſſa Meeſa\nne taps wairs no Uhdens-Pluh-\ndeem iſdeldeta / nn Pluhdi to\nSenumi wairs ne maitahs."
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un DEews fazzija : Schi\nirr tahs Derribas Sihme / ko es\ndohmu starp man un starp jums/\nnn starp wiſſahin dsihwahin Diva-\nſchahm / kas ar jums irr us muh-\nschigeim Laikem."
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Mannu Warrawihſni\neſim es Padebbeſi lizzis / nn ta\nbuhs tahs Derribas Sihme starp\nmannis/ un starp tahs Semmes."
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un / kad es Padebbe-\nfis pahr to Semmi waddischu\nun ta Warrawihſne Padebbeſi\nrahdiſees/"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad peeminneschu es fa-\nwn Derrbu / kas irr starp man\nun starp jums / un starp wiſſahin\ndsihwahm Dwachahm / un starp\njeb furras Meeſas : un Uhdens-\nPluhdi ne nahks wairs wiſſu\nMeeſu famaitaht."
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad nu buhs ta Warra-\nwihſne Padebbeſi / nn es ceſkat-\niſchohs to / peeminnedains tahs\nmuhſchigas Derribas starp Dee-\nwa/ un starp wiſſahin dsihwahm\nDwachahm / jebfurra Meeſa /\nkas wirs Semmes irr."
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un DEews fazzija uhs\nNoü: Schi irr tahs Derribas\nSih-"
    }
  ],
